    <h2>About This Project</h2>
    <p>
      This website accompanies a working paper on the cost-effectiveness of ESG integration in 
      university endowment funds. The research is conducted at the 
      <strong>Tinbergen Institute</strong> and is inspired by the work of 
      Aragon, Jiang, Joenväärä, and Tiu (JFE 2025).
    </p>

